{"h3a69eff9g8c43g43c6g9004gaaf7cedb36b2": ["Baretha - look what wanders near.", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "e2ea4562-ed89-c492-7683-0d6a0e415c48"], "hbfa86b85gbe5bg4cbag96a9g269abffb8d53": ["Child of Vlaakith. Be still, and listen.", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "c75e52b0-cbc1-1eac-36f5-2c1aac57f42c"], "h49d429f2g4c85g4563g9c45gaee2048d2daf": ["Hear me, knight. I must...", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "12ec3361-399e-85fd-2f13-05403d4f3e1d"], "h23913da5g8608g4cc8g8658g7f8e298e4df5": ["Do you not honour the command of a <i>kith'rak</i>, young one?", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "f5784115-57a3-c839-140f-96cc9d87f814"], "h08a63c0eg7efag4ccega61cgc7a8fa1611b5": ["It is not your time to speak.", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "b0bc144e-31c6-826b-a3da-5a887d3a1f36"], "h83d57331g60bag4107g88cagcf0d761d15ae": ["You do not understand. I heed Vlaakith's call.", "58a69333-40bf-8358-1d17-fff240d7fb12", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "23f1e294-3ee5-265e-67ec-475ac4c0fa6f"], "h49066db5g5dabg443egb624g5289b49bcb03": ["And yet you do not heed her <i>kith'rak's</i> command.", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "0f92bbec-60b4-21ca-2114-1c1fdc4220fc"], "h12513e8eg9f5bg4c48gb0c6g7c1166b60cc5": ["Few of our Queen's children prove so stubborn.", "2adce2df-0799-49dc-b867-ba7ca21e9aea", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Plains\\PLA_GithChokepoint_AD_LaezelWithKnight.html", "62cf6991-b245-fc9c-f18c-7f402da8f048"]}